originalText.text:
I've been using hair extensions for nearly a decade, but unfortunately, they've taken a toll on my hair's health. Recently, I discovered a novel technique known as "ice fusion extensions" and was eager to try it. Despite the holiday rush, I struggled to find a stylist in my area who could do it before Christmas.

That's when Elena and Victoria, two incredibly kind and accommodating stylists, came to my rescue. They went out of their way to fit me into their busy schedule. Not only did they assist me in selecting the perfect shade to complement my natural hair, but they also skillfully applied the new extensions.

The transformation has been remarkable. For the first time in years, I am thrilled with the appearance of my hair. These new extensions have given me a fresh, revitalized look that I absolutely adore. I'm immensely grateful for the skill and kindness of Elena and Victoria in helping me achieve this fantastic result.

originalText.text: I have very fine hair and have been  bleaching my hair for 30 years so it's difficult for me to achieve length and volume with out extensions. I have been using extensions for many years, and most  recently had keratin bond extensions for 2.5 years.however,  I wanted to try this new ice micro bond technique , and after doing much research i found Elena (ice babes ) on instagram / online . I looked at her work, was very impressed, and decided to make an appt with her . Elena and her assistant Victoria were nothing short of amazing . They were professional, kind , caring , and listened carefully to what my hair goals are . The attention to detail and intricate work is truly an art and a talent not mastered by many . The outcome of my hair is perfection . I love my hair extension from ice babes - the quality of hair , the length , volume and color matches perfectly. It looks natural like it grew from my scalp . This service is a high quality luxury , and i highly recommend using ice babes for your extensions and hair needs.  You will not be disappointed. 5 stars ‚≠êÔ∏è ‚ù§Ô∏è
